 \n\u201cMLK: Now is the Time\u201d is an immersive journey that explores key themes of Dr. King's speech and highlights systemic inequities that persist in our society. Through first-person stories and interactions, \u201cMLK: Now is the Time\u201d drops you into a thoroughly modern interpretation of a contemporary March on Washington that will inform and inspire a new generation of activists."}]}, "developer_name": "Flight School Studio", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "http://time.com/nowisthetime/privacypolicy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "TIME Immersive", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "http://time.com/nowisthetime/", "category": "ENTERTAINMENT", "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_MOST", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "362692211442873", "context_category": "APPS"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "434961926215971"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["EDUCATIONAL", "DOCUMENTARY_HISTORY", "EXPERIENCE_360_NON_GAME"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["HAND_TRACKING", "OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "496618139167721"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 1, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "575852274419335"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "575852274419335"}, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": [{"start_time": 1673532060, "status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "575852274419335"}]}, "liveChannel": {"nodes": [{"latest_supported_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "id": "6227997767290011", "version": "1.0.1-670645-1"}, "id": "629698568241830", "channel_name": "LIVE"}]}, "is_for_oculus_keys_only": false, "prim